name: KLM 777-206ER [PH-BQO] INAUGURAL Landing In Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
KLM, you are awesome.

Here is the inaugural flight of KLM's 777-200ER into Calgary International Airport, operating 3x a week for the summer season. Sorry for the shakiness, it was really windy outside. I plan to catch these birds several times over the summer ;) I hope you enjoy, and watch in 1080p for better quality!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
